Package main.spaces.MagentaSpace

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuyAHouseSpace
    Represents the Magenta Space - Buy a House Space allows the Player to have an option whether to buy a house by choosing from the house Deck or not
    CollegeCareerChoiceSpace
    Represents the Magenta Space - College Career Choice Space gets the top 2 Career Card and Salary Card from their respective Decks are shown to the Player where in the Player will choose one of each and return the others.
    GetMarriedSpace
    Represents the Magenta Space - Get Married Space where a player marries and depending on the Player's random generated number, he/she pays a certain amount of money for the wedding gift.
    HaveBabySpace
    Represents the Magenta Space - Have a Baby or Twin Space where when a Married Player lands here, he/she collects $5000 for each child from each players.
    JobSearchSpace
    Represents the Magenta Space - Job Search Space which allows the Player to choose a new career
    MagentaSpace
    Represents the Magenta Space which is inherited by all other classes for Magenta Space.
    WhichPathSpace
    Represents the Magenta Space - Which Path Space which is a junction where players can choose to continue the current path or switch to another one
